'''印度理工學院'''（{{lang-hi|भारतीय प्रौद्योगिकी संस्थान}}，{{lang-en|Indian Institutes of Technology}}，簡稱''IIT''），是由[[印度|印度]][[政府|政府]]所建設的自治[[工程|工程]]與[[技術|技術]]教学、研究學院，位于印度各地<ref>{{cite web|title=More IIT seats possible this year|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/More-IIT-seats-possible-this-year/articleshow/52306266.cms|accessdate=|author=|date=2016|format=|publisher=Times of India|language=|archive-date=2020-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200115110743/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/More-IIT-seats-possible-this-year/articleshow/52306266.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。印度理工学院受印度法律[[1961年理工学院法|1961年理工学院法]]管辖，其认定學院为「国家重要机关」（Institutes of National Importance）<ref name="IIT Act As amended till 20122">{{cite web|title=IIT Act (As amended till 2012|url=http://www.iitg.ac.in/rti/links/acts_statutes_iitguwahati.pdf|access-date=10 September 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203221638/http://www.iitg.ac.in/rti/links/acts_statutes_iitguwahati.pdf|archive-date=2013-12-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，共有23所<ref name="hindustantimes.com">{{cite web|title=Problem of plenty: As IITs multiply, the brand value diminishes|url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/higherstudies/as-number-of-iits-increase-their-brand-value-diminishes/article1-1363608.aspx|date=29 June 2015|publisher=Hindustan Times|accessdate=2020-08-08|archive-date=2015-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150831075125/http://www.hindustantimes.com/higherstudies/as-number-of-iits-increase-their-brand-value-diminishes/article1-1363608.aspx|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，被认为是印度顶尖的理工学院<ref>{{Cite web|title=JEE Advanced 2020 Exam on May 3, Check total number of seats in 23 IITs for B.Tech and other UG courses here|url=https://www.timesnownews.com/education/article/jee-advanced-2020-exam-on-may-3-check-total-number-of-seats-in-23-iits-for-b-tech-and-other-ug-courses-here/554442|accessdate=2020-08-08|work=www.timesnownews.com|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201215165647/https://www.timesnownews.com/education/article/jee-advanced-2020-exam-on-may-3-check-total-number-of-seats-in-23-iits-for-b-tech-and-other-ug-courses-here/554442|dead-url=no}}</ref>。每所 IIT 均为自治机关，但所有学院有共同的理事会（IIT Council），负责其行政管理。

至2021年，印度理工学院有学生16,232人。最早的印度理工學院1951年創立在[[西孟加拉邦|西孟加拉邦]]。創建這些學院的主要原因，是印度政府剛從[[大英帝國|大英帝國]]得到獨立，認為必需要培養及訓練[[科學家|科學家]]和[[工程師|工程師]]。

