== 入学选拔（JEE） ==
截至2021年，有23所印度理工学院，该年的学位约16,232人。印度理工学院主要通过入学考试选拔，即 JEE （Joint Entrance Exam，联合入学考试）。JEE 分为两轮：JEE Main 及 JEE Advanced<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=IIT success kiss from 2 Telugu powerhouses {{!}} Hyderabad News - Times of India|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/hyderabad/iit-success-kiss-from-2-telugu-powerhouses/articleshow/64534793.cms|accessdate=2020-08-08|author=Nirupa Vatyam|date=|last=|first=|format=|work=The Times of India|publisher=|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612171247/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/hyderabad/iit-success-kiss-from-2-telugu-powerhouses/articleshow/64534793.cms|archive-date=2018-06-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其中，JEE Main 的考试成绩可以用于国立理工学院、国立信息技术学院等大学的入学，也同时负责筛选得以参加 JEE Advanced 的考生。IIT 的入学则取决于 JEE Advanced 的成绩。2018 年，有 100 万人参加 JEE Main 考试<ref>{{Cite web|title=IIT JEE Main 2018: 10.5 lakh students appeared for the examination - Times of India|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/education/news/iit-jee-main-2018-10-5-lakh-students-appeared-for-the-examination/articleshow/63677318.cms|website=The Times of India|access-date=2019-08-15|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225072132/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/education/news/iit-jee-main-2018-10-5-lakh-students-appeared-for-the-examination/articleshow/63677318.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其中 22.4 万允许参加 JEE Advanced 考试<ref>{{Cite web|title=Eligibility Criteria For Indian Nationals (including PIO/OCI For Appearing In Jee (Advanced) 2018|url=https://www.jeeadv.ac.in/Eligibility-Criteria.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180907125209/https://www.jeeadv.ac.in/Eligibility-Criteria.html|archive-date=2018-09-07|accessdate=2020-08-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，竞争 11,279 个 IIT 学位。

除 JEE 外，学生一般还需在高中毕业考试（Class XII Board examination）中分数值在 75% 以上，或成绩排列为前 20%，但在 2020 年暂时取消此要求，只需高中毕业考试合格<ref>{{Cite web|title=JEE Advanced 2020: Criteria of 75% marks in Class 12 for admissions in IIT removed for this year, says HRD minister|url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/education/jee-advanced-2020-criteria-of-75-marks-in-class-12-for-admissions-in-iit-removed-for-this-year-says-hrd-minister/story-bnjDUZEbj6M5mg3kY7ivnK.html|accessdate=2020-08-08|date=2020-07-17|work=Hindustan Times|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110181155/https://www.hindustantimes.com/education/jee-advanced-2020-criteria-of-75-marks-in-class-12-for-admissions-in-iit-removed-for-this-year-says-hrd-minister/story-bnjDUZEbj6M5mg3kY7ivnK.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

IIT 对部分弱势群体实行优惠性配额制度，设有15%的[[表列种姓和表列部落|表列种姓]]保留席位、7.5%的[[表列种姓和表列部落|表列部落]]保留席位、5%的残障人士（Persons with Disability）保留席位<ref name=":0" />。此外，IIT 专设 20%的额外学位给予女性考生<ref name=":0" />。

